							<h4>By rescuing food, we&#x2019;re helping create lasting, positive change for people and for our planet.</h4>
						<div class="green_underline small"></div>
				
					<span class="text"><ul ><li>We&rsquo;re reducing our country&rsquo;s environmental footprint by keeping surplus food out of landfills and reducing harmful greenhouse gases, a leading source of human-caused climate change &nbsp;</li><li>We&rsquo;re creating an efficient food supply chain by optimizing the resources that go into producing and distributing food, like energy, water and land &nbsp;</li><li>We&rsquo;re feeding people experiencing hunger in communities across Canada </li></ul><p>Our job of rescuing food is supported by our programs like Harvest Kitchens and Feeding Our Future, and our ongoing work in education, training, and research.&nbsp;</p></span>

					
				</div>
			</div>

		</div>

	</div>

</div>


    








<div class="container-fluid image_text_cta_container squiggly_top white alternate_image   ">

	<div class="container max_body_width_narrow image_text_cta_inner_container">

		<div class="row">

			<div class="col image_container fade ">
				<div class="frame orange_bg"></div>
				<img src="/SecondHarvest/media/Images/About%20Us/WWD_Sustainability_Cropped.png" class="fade w_left_offset" alt="" />
			</div>

			<div class="col text_container ml-auto">
				<div class="text_inner_container fade w_margin_offset">

				
					<span class="text"><p >We&rsquo;re here to create meaningful impact for people and the planet, so we&rsquo;re playing our part to meet Canada&rsquo;s commitment to the United Nations&rsquo; 2030 Agenda for Sustainable Development, including Goal 12: Responsible Consumption and Production, Goal 13: Climate Action and Goal 2: Zero Hunger. &nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p>Climate change, food waste and hunger are challenging issues, and it takes drive and the passion to face them head on. Realizing our vision of No Waste. No Hunger. can only be done when we all believe that it can &ndash; and will &ndash; be achieved.</p></span>

					
				</div>
			</div>

		</div>

	</div>

</div>


    



	</div>

</div>



		









<div class="container-fluid cta_generic_container default">
